    "In particular, j consists of a single layer of 2 j parallel CNOTs where the targets of the CNOTs are fresh ancillae.",
    "This is illustrated in Fig. 12 and described in Algorithm 3.",
    "Notably, while the total number of qubits is c and the depth is ⌈log 2 (c)⌉, most of the ancillae need not be allocated until close to the end of the protocol, and thus the spacetime allocation is Θ(c), rather than O(c log(c)).= = α |0⟩ + β |1⟩ COPY 8 0 1 2 α|0 8 ⟩ + β|1 8 ⟩ |0⟩ |0⟩ |0⟩ |0⟩ |0⟩ |0⟩ |0⟩Figure 12: Example circuit implementing state copy subroutine for c = 8 qubits.",
